# Cloudflare Pages — fallback rewrites.
#
# LaserForge is a single-page app with no client-side router (everything
# lives at "/"), so this file is mostly defensive: it ensures that any
# deep link or refresh on a non-existent path still loads index.html
# instead of returning Cloudflare's default 404.
#
# `200` (not `301`/`302`) is a rewrite, not a redirect — the URL stays
# put and the SPA hydrates from index.html.

/*  /index.html  200
